698→### 2.5 GPS Confidence Scoring Formula
699→
700→```
701→GPS_CONFIDENCE_SCORE (0-100)
702→==============================
703→
704→Starts at 100, deductions applied:
705→
706→Signal                              Deduction    Condition
707→────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
708→Mock location detected              -50          Client reports isMocked=true
709→GPS accuracy = 0                    -20          Unrealistic for consumer device
710→GPS accuracy > 100m (non-low-end)   -10          Poor GPS fix
711→GPS-EXIF mismatch > threshold       -30          Photo taken elsewhere
712→No EXIF GPS (non-low-end)           -15          Cannot cross-validate
713→No EXIF GPS (low-end device)        -5           Expected for feature phones
714→IP-GPS mismatch > 50km              -15          Submitting from different city
715→Impossible travel (>200 km/h)       -40          Cannot physically move that fast
716→Suspicious travel (>80 km/h)        -15          Unusual for Douala
717→GPS time drift > 30 seconds         -10          Stale GPS fix or clock issue
718→No accelerometer data (non-low-end) -5           Possible emulator
719→No motion detected during capture   -5           Stationary spoofing
720→
721→Bonuses:
722→EXIF GPS matches submission GPS     +5           Strong corroboration
723→All three sources agree (GPS/EXIF/IP) +5         Maximum confidence
724→
725→Final score = clamp(score, 0, 100)
726→```
