2061→### 5.6 Integration with Teammate 2's Confidence Score
2062→
2063→The fraud risk score modifies the confidence score as follows:
2064→
2065→```typescript
2066→// Extension to Teammate 2's computeConfidenceScore function
2067→
2068→function computeConfidenceScoreWithFraud(
2069→  point: ProjectedPoint,
2070→  referenceDate: Date,
2071→  fraudRiskScore: number  // From computeFraudRiskScore
2072→): number {
2073→  // Compute base confidence score (Teammate 2's formula)
2074→  const baseScore = computeConfidenceScore(point, referenceDate);
2075→
2076→  // Apply fraud penalty
2077→  // fraudRiskScore 0-25: no penalty
2078→  // fraudRiskScore 26-50: -5 to -15 points
2079→  // fraudRiskScore 51-75: -15 to -30 points
2080→  // fraudRiskScore 76-100: -30 to -50 points
2081→  let fraudPenalty = 0;
2082→  if (fraudRiskScore > 75) {
2083→    fraudPenalty = 30 + Math.round((fraudRiskScore - 75) * 0.8);
2084→  } else if (fraudRiskScore > 50) {
2085→    fraudPenalty = 15 + Math.round((fraudRiskScore - 50) * 0.6);
2086→  } else if (fraudRiskScore > 25) {
2087→    fraudPenalty = 5 + Math.round((fraudRiskScore - 25) * 0.4);
2088→  }
2089→
2090→  return Math.max(0, Math.min(100, baseScore - fraudPenalty));
2091→}
2092→```
